T1  - The Labor Market Consequences of Student Loan Forbearance
AU  - Hamdi, Naser
AU  - Kalda, Ankit
AU  - Sovich, David
Y1  - 2025/09/10
PY  - 2025
DA  - 2025/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2023.04047
